\fs24 \cf5 \cb31 \strokec5 Core Passive: Terminating Verdict\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\b0\fs21 \cf16 \cb31 \strokec16 When 
\f0\b \cf27 \strokec27 Chain Attack: Trick of Fate
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  hits an enemy or Hugo's attacks Stun an enemy, Hugo gains the 
\f0\b \cf27 \strokec27 Dark Abyss Reverb
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  state for 6s, and repeated triggers reset the duration. During this state, Hugo's CRIT Rate increases by 12% and CRIT DMG increases by 25%.\cb1 \
\cb31 When there are 1/2 
\f0\b \cf27 \strokec27 Stun
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  characters in your squad, Hugo's ATK increases by 
\f0\b \cf32 \strokec32 300
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16 /
\f0\b \cf32 \strokec32 900
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16 .\cb1 \
\cb31 When the Finishing Move of 
\f0\b \cf27 \strokec27 EX Special Attack: Soul Hunter - Punishment
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  or 
\f0\b \cf27 \strokec27 Ultimate: Blaspheme
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  hits an enemy while they are Stunned, it triggers the 
\f0\b \cf27 \strokec27 Totalize
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  effect, increasing the DMG Multiplier of the skill's Finishing Move by 
\f0\b \cf32 \strokec32 1,000%
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16 . Additionally, the 
\f0\b \cf27 \strokec27 Totalize
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  effect further increases the skill's DMG multiplier based on the remaining Stun time of the enemy when triggered: for each remaining second of Stun time from the portion that is less than or equal to 5s, the skill's DMG multiplier increases by 
\f0\b \cf32 \strokec32 280%
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16 ; for each remaining second of Stun time from the portion between 5 and 15s, the skill's DMG multiplier increases by 
\f0\b \cf32 \strokec32 100%
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16 . The total increase can raise the skill's DMG multiplier by a maximum of 
\f0\b \cf32 \strokec32 3,400%
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16 .\cb1 \
\cb31 After Hugo triggers the 
\f0\b \cf27 \strokec27 Totalize
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  effect, the enemy's Stunned state will immediately end. Based on the remaining Stun time at the moment 
\f0\b \cf27 \strokec27 Totalize
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  is triggered, a certain amount of Daze will be accumulated. For every second of Stun time remaining, 5% Daze is accumulated, up to a maximum Daze equivalent to 25% of the enemy's maximum Daze.\cb1 \
\cb31 When 
\f0\b \cf27 \strokec27 EX Special Attack: Soul Hunter - Punishment
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  hits an enemy, if the enemy is not Stunned, the Daze accumulated by the skill increases by 20%.\cb1 \
